          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1641813335997-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>gnocchi </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the gnocchi for 3 min or until it begins to rise to the top of the pot</p><p>Once done, drain the gnocchi and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy cooking water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1641813340649-x200.jpg",
