            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have slightly softened, add the <strong>tomato frito</strong> and half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> the <strong>black olives</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining olives for another recipe! </p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the olives are warmed through – these are your <strong>Mediterranean vegetables</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1641813344584-x200.jpg",
