      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate the<strong> cheddar flavour block</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
