        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained gnocchi</strong> through the Mediterranean vegetables and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and stir for 1-2 min until the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>Mediterranean vegetable gnocchi</strong></p><p>Tip: If the sauce is looking a little dry, add a splash of the reserved starchy cooking water</p>",
